# Project Rules for Hills Mac Repair Site

## Git Workflow
- Always commit and push changes to GitHub after completing any task
- Use descriptive commit messages that explain what was changed
- Run: git add . && git commit -m "message" && git push (or separate commands on Windows)

## Deployment
- This site uses Netlify with automatic deployments from GitHub
- After pushing to GitHub, Netlify will automatically build and deploy the site
